'''Christine Hewett''' was an actress who portrayed the "space girl" in a blue bodysuit in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']]. Her character was later identified as [[Brea Tonnika]] of the [[Tonnika sisters]], also known as [[Shada D'ukal]]. The actress was a guest at [[Celebration III]].<ref name="Insider 95" /> She died on [[September 18]], [[2007]].<ref name="RIP Christine Hewitt" />

